info.name: Test REST API MS-Task with param
info.description:
Common methods for _**CRUD**_ applications.

- All products Request: get all products from the database. You can specify the key in the request or check the box next to the parameter and specify the value you need in the corresponding column.EndFragment
    
- One product Request: get a single product by id.
    
- Error GET request: error message when receiving a non-existent product.
    
- New product add Request: add a new product. Data is in the body.
    
- New error Request: error message when new product data is invalid
    
- Update product with some id: change an existing product by id. Data is in the body.
    
- Delete product with some id: delete a product by id.
    
- Error delete Request: Error when deleting a non-existent product.
